room_title: Escape room "The Enchanted Potion Room" by Elusive Escape Rooms in Wisconsin Dells
room_address: 1425 Wisconsin Dells Parkway Suite 3 Wisconsin Dells, WI 53965
room_description: Witches and wizards alike, welcome to another day at your school of Enchantment. You find your beloved professor Barnabus under a spell for which you have little knowledge. You know this is the work of the wicked professor, Bloodwynd. You sneak into his office to find the correct way to brew a counter-curse to free your professor. If you don’t find the proper formula within an hour, then I’m afraid the potion’s effects will be permanent!
